1. Osmosys DB connects to Kafka topic.
2. Kafka retrieves comprehensive system metrics (Host Name, CPU, Memory, Uptime, Network, Disk).
3. A dedicated Kafka topic filters and stores uptime data.
4. Scheduled cron job extracts and updates uptime data every 10 minutes.
5. Data is transferred to InfluxDB for efficient storage.
6. InfluxDB integrates with visualization tools like Grafana or Tableau for data presentation.
